00:54:35,833 --> 00:54:36,933
Ibu?

481
00:54:37,490 --> 00:54:38,590
Ya.

482
00:54:39,123 --> 00:54:40,223
Ibu di sini.

483
00:54:40,951 --> 00:54:44,613
Ibu sekarang takkan
pergi lagi, kan?

484
00:55:29,740 --> 00:55:32,121
Aku mau ikut Ibu.

485
00:55:32,138 --> 00:55:34,438
Ibu harus ke tempat lain.

486
00:55:34,974 --> 00:55:37,160
Apa aku boleh ikut Ibu?

487
00:55:37,576 --> 00:55:40,675
Ah-ram, Ibu akan segera datang.

488
00:55:41,990 --> 00:55:43,552
Cepat masuk mobil.

489
00:55:43,552 --> 00:55:46,746
Kalau tak menurut,
Ibu takkan datang.

490
00:55:48,896 --> 00:55:50,472
Kau anak pintar.

491
00:55:50,771 --> 00:55:55,753
Kalau kau tak sakit dan
mau sekolah, Ibu akan datang.

492
00:56:08,435 --> 00:56:11,469
Tiga hari lagi, Ibu sungguh
akan datang, kan?

493
00:56:17,411 --> 00:56:18,597
Ayo.

494
00:56:34,349 --> 00:56:36,332
Kau akan pergi begitu saja?

495
00:56:36,904 --> 00:56:40,636
Tolong jaga Ah-Jin
dan Ah-ram baik-baik.

496
00:56:41,904 --> 00:56:43,004
Tunggu.

497
00:56:43,099 --> 00:56:44,199
Ibu Ah-Jin.

498
00:56:55,662 --> 00:56:57,695
Jangan mengharapkan
perceraian yang mudah.

499
00:57:00,529 --> 00:57:03,918
Aku takkan meminta hak asuh.

500
00:57:05,177 --> 00:57:10,652
Tapi kalau kau merasa terlalu sulit,
aku akan membesarkan mereka.

501
00:57:11,724 --> 00:57:14,291
Setidaknya sampai
Ah-ram masuk SD.

502
00:57:15,443 --> 00:57:17,771
Sekarang bukan ibu
yang membesarkan anak.

503
00:57:17,771 --> 00:57:19,071
Uang yang membesarkan.

504
00:58:49,185 --> 00:58:50,285
Min-young.

505
00:58:53,951 --> 00:58:56,988
Sudah kubilang jangan pernah
menemuinya lagi!

506
00:58:57,107 --> 00:58:58,207
Min-young--

507
00:58:58,240 --> 00:59:01,340
Kalian tahu
perbuatan kalian sekarang?

508
00:59:02,193 --> 00:59:07,183
Kalian menghancurkan kehidupanku
dan kehidupan anak kita!

509
00:59:10,341 --> 00:59:11,575
Kau tak mengerti?

510
00:59:12,341 --> 00:59:14,441
Kau tak mengerti ucapanku?

511
00:59:16,873 --> 00:59:20,402
Jung-woo, aku hamil.

512
00:59:21,459 --> 00:59:23,464
Aku mengandung anakmu.

513
00:59:29,451 --> 00:59:30,839
Hamil?

514
00:59:49,607 --> 00:59:51,543
Pasti ini akhirnya.

515
00:59:52,865 --> 00:59:54,565
Di ujung tebing...

516
00:59:55,826 --> 00:59:57,526
tujuan akhir kami...

517
01:00:07,138 --> 01:00:08,410
Ji-eun...

518
01:00:22,794 --> 01:00:25,285
Ji-eun! Ji-eun, tunggu!

519
01:00:53,873 --> 01:00:56,306
Meski aku mencintai
dengan segenap hati...

520
01:00:58,037 --> 01:01:00,464
Meski kuserahkan hidupku...

521
01:01:04,677 --> 01:01:07,886
Satu orang yang
tak dapat kumiliki...

522
01:01:11,201 --> 01:01:12,301
adalah kau...

523
01:01:53,123 --> 01:01:57,523
